{"type": "article", "id": 25142, "title": "有蚯蚓堆肥系统的花盆", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-08T07:02:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 79, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607123109nIUPcrHTwV8KsiJo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个花盆引入了蚯蚓堆肥生态系统，三个叠放的陶罐是打通的，它们构成了树桩的形状，而带植物的花盆则单独放在了最上面。蚯蚓和果皮等废料放在下面三个陶罐的土壤中，蚯蚓可以加快土壤分解并产出可作为肥料的液体，同时也慢慢让带植物的花盆下沉，当它完全下沉时则提醒你添加新的果皮，然后不断循环。这是一个环保而高效的种植方式，<a href=\"http://maoraharon.com/#MoM\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071231064fkgLBmApj0NWdEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060712310661GBH7z9ZxiNofQw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071231078MJqSHduDoLNYQ72.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123107acuqRWFp7vl0bxd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123108SinE1hG3ICJl8UYu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607123108vhPkVMFfjsYu96ZL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}